" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Nordic lower: Starting position",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 351px; height: 468px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The Nordic lower exercise strengthens the hamstring muscles and many other muscles of the posterior kinetic chain. Maintain the thighs and torso in a straight line throughout the exercise.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Courtesy of Karl Fields, MD; Spencer Copland, MD; and John Tipton, MD.",
"    </div>",
